### Get all the drinks
GET http://localhost:8080/api/drinks


### Create a drink
POST http://localhost:8080/api/drinks
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Vanilla Latte",
  "description": "Espresso with vanilla syrup and milk",
  "price": 550,
  "categoryId": 1,
  "tags": ["hot", "sweet"],
  "images": ["vanilla_latte_main.jpg"]
}

###

### Update a drink
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/drinks/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Vanilla Iced Latte",
  "description": "Chilled espresso with vanilla syrup",
  "price": 575,
  "categoryId": 1,
  "tags": ["iced", "sweet"],
  "images": ["vanilla_iced_latte.jpg"]
}

###

### Delete a drink (soft delete)
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/drinks/1

### =========================================
### BASE URL
### =========================================
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080


### =========================================
### 1️⃣ NOT FOUND → Get non-existent drink
### =========================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/drinks/99999


### =========================================
### 2️⃣ VALIDATION ERROR → Create drink (bad input)
### =========================================
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/drinks
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "",
  "price": -5,
  "categoryId": null
}


### =========================================
### 3️⃣ CREATE A VALID DRINK (SETUP)
### =========================================
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/drinks
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Iced Latte",
  "price": 500,
  "categoryId": 1
}


### =========================================
### 4️⃣ BUSINESS RULE → Duplicate drink
### =========================================
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/drinks
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "iced latte",
  "price": 500,
  "categoryId": 1
}


### =========================================
### 5️⃣ NOT FOUND → Invalid category
### =========================================
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/drinks
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Cold Brew",
  "price": 600,
  "categoryId": 999
}


### =========================================
### 6️⃣ UPDATE → Non-existent drink
### =========================================
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/drinks/999
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Espresso",
  "price": 400,
  "categoryId": 1
}


### =========================================
### 7️⃣ DELETE → Non-existent drink
### =========================================
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/drinks/999


### =========================================
### 8️⃣ DELETE → Already inactive drink (optional)
### Run twice to trigger 409 on second call
### =========================================
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/drinks/1


